snippet.title: Atari Karts (Jaguar) - Part 1
snippet.description:
Atari's kart racing game for the Jaguar may not be Mario Kart, but it is a fun little game with some cool tunes. Here I compete in the Carleton Cup. This is part 1 of 2.
